---------------------------------------------------------------------------+
Polls Plugin 2.1                                                          
---------------------------------------------------------------------------+
functions.inc                                                             
                                                                          
This file does two things: 1) it implements the necessary Geeklog Plugin  
API method and 2) implements all the common code needed by the Polls      
plugin' PHP files.                                                        
